**why —** Because the film needs its objectified girl — and, read with a little mercy, a girl with exactly one door.
**how —** By treating the star quarterback as a ticket, and the whipped cream as the plan executed.

**the seal —** Football is my way out of this town. I'm not the villain — I'm a girl with one exit and a clock on it.

